<div id="pf4056" class="pf w55 h2ce" data-page-no="4056"><div class="pc pc4056 w55 h2ce"><div class="t m2b1 x3 h5 y2cbd ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 9 May 22 - 28 </div><div class="t m1ac2 xb7 h78 y213a ff3 fs2a fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Model of </div><div class="t m161a xb7 h78 y7c6 ff3 fs2a fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sociableness </div><div class="t m711 x11 h5 yf1d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Jesus increased in wisdom and </div><div class="t m7c0 x3 h5 y922 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">stature, and in favour with God and </div><div class="t m833 x3 h5 y777 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">man&quot; (Luke 2:52). </div><div class="t maea x11 h35 ye44 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Somehow through the centuries an </div><div class="t ma93 x3 h35 ye79 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">unfortunate falsehood has infiltrated </div><div class="t m1471 x3 h35 yf23 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Christian church. It rears its </div><div class="t m24c x3 h35 yd95 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">perverse head enough to confuse </div><div class="t ma0e x3 h35 yf27 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">serious people who indeed want to </div><div class="t m740 x3 h35 y8b1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">follow in the footsteps of their Master. </div><div class="t m7be x3 h35 yc78 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The perversity: that religion made </div><div class="t m422 x3 h35 y83d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Jesus gloomy. </div><div class="t m724 x56 h35 y7c8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Although there is no place in the </div><div class="t m12c x1c h35 y1272 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">serious Christian&apos;s life for frivolity and </div><div class="t m238 x1c h35 y777 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">silly laughter, no one in the world has a </div><div class="t m2df x1c h35 yec2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">better right to be cheerful and to enjoy </div><div class="t mb5b x1c h35 y73c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">innocent laughter. There is something </div><div class="t m85 x1c h35 yd38 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">very chilling about people who do not </div><div class="t m3a